{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNMapView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"didDeselectAnnotationView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotationView"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view containing the annotation."}]}],"name":"mapView"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The annotation view that was deselected."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotationView"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can use this method to track changes in the selection state of annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"views."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"This method is only called for annotation views. To track changes in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"selection state of all annotations, including those associated with static","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotation images, implement ","type":"text"},{"code":"-mapView:didDeselectAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", which is called","type":